sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User as NguoiDung
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant AuthMW as Middleware_XacThuc
participant PermMW as Middleware_PhanQuyen
participant RoleSvc as RolePermissionService

Note over User,RoleSvc: Chặng 2 - Luồng từ chối
User->>Gateway: Request private
Gateway->>AuthMW: Verify token
alt Token sai hoặc hết hạn
  AuthMW-->>User: 401 Unauthorized
else Token hợp lệ
  Gateway->>PermMW: Kiểm tra quyền
  PermMW->>RoleSvc: check permission
  alt Thiếu context hoặc không đủ quyền
    RoleSvc-->>PermMW: allowed=false
    PermMW-->>User: 403 Forbidden
  else Lỗi role service
    PermMW-->>User: 403 fail-closed
  end
end
